Block of code: Set of instructions
-	It will execute only that specific condition is true 
Condition: An expression that evaluates the result(True or False)
Ex: console.log(5>6)
Methods:
-	If: only one possible condition. if condition is true it will execute otherwise it will skip.

-	If-else
-	Else if
-	Switch
-	Ternary operator


